A former Deputy National Chairman of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) Chief Bode George, has lost his son, Dipo.

According to reports, Dipo, who was 42-years-old, died in the early hours of Thursday after a long battle with an undisclosed ailment. 

He died at a hospital in Ikoyi, Lagos state. 

